{"ec":"ET00098080","t":"Suspense ","img":"https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/movies/images/mobile/thumbnail/large/suspense-et00098080-06-03-2019-10-54-37.jpg","og":"https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/movies/images/mobile/listing/xxlarge/suspense-et00098080-06-03-2019-10-54-37.jpg","d":"The film revolves around six close friends Arav, Shikha, Abhishek, Hetal, Vikki and Vidyut who work with different organizations, live in different cities but manage to meet once a year. \n\n<br/><br/>The friends plan to meet again for a vacation. Meanwhile, Arav realizes that the stories that he has been narrating to her six-year-old niece are turning into a reality. He recalls one such incident where he had made a story about him and his friends vacationing in a bungalow and the owner wanted to kill them. What if that story comes true? Will Arav be able to amend the damage done before its too late? Will he be able to save his friends?\n\n","rd":"2019-03-08","rt":110,"ct":"A","g":["Suspense","Thriller"],"l":["Hindi"],"f":["2D"],"i":null,"cast":[["Vikram Mastal","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/vikram-mastal-1266146-08-03-2019-02-17-31.jpg"],["Antra Banarjee","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/antra-banarjee-1266147-08-03-2019-02-39-02.jpg"],["Madhumita Bishwas","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/madhumita-bishwas-1266150-08-03-2019-02-24-55.jpg"]],"crew":{"d":[["Ajay Yadav","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/ajay-yadav-29893-08-03-2019-02-42-34.jpg"]],"p":[],"m":[],"c":[],"e":[]}}
